Tower Group Says April, May Storms Cost Insurer $8 Million

-- B y   B r o o k e   S u t h e r l a n d
-- 
2011-06-27T20:09:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/tower-group-says-april-may-storms-cost-insurer-8-million.html
Tower Group Inc. (TWGP)  reported pretax
losses of $8 million tied to natural disasters in April and May.  Increased claims costs will reduce second-quarter earnings
per share by 13 cents, the New York-based insurer said in a
statement distributed by  Business Wire  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brooke Sutherland in New York at 
 Bsutherland5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  